    <item>
      <title>因涉嫌加沙虐待而被捕的士兵动摇了以色列的战争团结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/soldier-arrests-for-alleged-gaza-abuse-shake-israel-s-war-unity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列国防部长指责政府中的极右翼同行鼓励抗议逮捕涉嫌虐待巴勒斯坦囚犯的士兵，从而破坏了国家的战争努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/soldier-arrests-for-alleged-gaza-abuse-shake-israel-s-war-unity</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 12:42:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非寻求与欧盟就碳税进行谈判，称其损害金砖国家利益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/south-africa-seeks-eu-talks-on-carbon-tax-it-says-hurts-brics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非将与欧盟商讨对碳密集型进口产品征税的计划，并称此举将损害金砖国家的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/south-africa-seeks-eu-talks-on-carbon-tax-it-says-hurts-brics</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 12:35:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国向欧盟表示希望在 2025 年春季进行安全协定谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/uk-tells-eu-it-wants-security-pact-negotiations-in-spring-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·史塔默 (Keir Starmer) 领导的英国新政府向欧盟表示，希望在 2025 年春季就国防和安全协议展开实质性谈判，这意味着不太可能快速达成协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/uk-tells-eu-it-wants-security-pact-negotiations-in-spring-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 12:09:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>白俄罗斯称被定罪的德国人向总统请求赦免</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/belarus-says-convicted-german-asked-president-for-pardon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[因代表乌克兰从事“雇佣军活动”而在白俄罗斯被判处死刑的德国公民里科·克里格 (Rico Krieger) 已请求白俄罗斯总统亚历山大·卢卡申科 (Alexander Lukashenko) 赦免他。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/belarus-says-convicted-german-asked-president-for-pardon</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 11:54:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国增加可再生能源预算至创纪录的 15 亿英镑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/uk-boosting-budget-for-renewables-to-record-1-5-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国将在即将举行的拍卖会上将对新可再生能源发电的支持增加至创纪录的 15 亿英镑（19 亿美元），这向政府绿色计划的关键行业发出了明确信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/uk-boosting-budget-for-renewables-to-record-1-5-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 10:11:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯加大力度在摇摆州与特朗普竞争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/harris-team-sees-expanded-electoral-map-in-race-against-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯于周二在亚特兰大举行集会，拉开在更广泛的战场州与共和党人唐纳德·特朗普竞争的序幕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/harris-team-sees-expanded-electoral-map-in-race-against-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国在美贸易协定中发挥主导作用或有助于限制芯片争端</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/south-korea-taps-us-trade-deal-to-prevent-chip-spats-with-japan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国将在美国主导的亚洲贸易协定中发挥引领作用，通过合作网络确保全球供应链的安全，这一作用也可能有助于限制与日本发生贸易争端的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/south-korea-taps-us-trade-deal-to-prevent-chip-spats-with-japan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉反对派称掌握选举舞弊的证据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/venezuela-s-machado-says-opposition-has-enough-proof-of-fraud</link>
      <description><![CDATA[领导反对总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗竞选活动的玛丽亚·科里娜·马查多表示，委内瑞拉反对派可以证明埃德蒙多·冈萨雷斯赢得了周日的选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/venezuela-s-machado-says-opposition-has-enough-proof-of-fraud</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 23:16:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国特使称美国支持尽早延长非洲贸易协定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/us-backs-early-extension-of-trade-pact-with-africa-envoy-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位特使表示，美国总统乔·拜登政府支持尽早延长一项计划，该计划将使 30 多个撒哈拉以南非洲国家能够保留进入世界最大经济体的免税资格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/us-backs-early-extension-of-trade-pact-with-africa-envoy-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 15:34:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
